name: Kamahachi
content:
Kamahachi was a human male travel guide. Along with Senshu, he helped Princess Misa and Jedi Knight Tsubaki reach a royal palace that the princess had been exiled from.
They took a dangerous path to avoid checkpoints, and the guides were awarded over 500 credits for their service, which included crossing the feared Place of the Gods. It was in this area that Kamahachi went missing. Tsubaki eventually found him, and both of them regrouped with Misa and Senshu in a nearby village.
When Tsubaki and Misa attempted to break into the palace and overthrow the Sith Lord Masago, Kamahachi and Senshu were both detained by guards and threatened by Masago.
